Package game

Class MazeConfigure

java.lang.Object
game.MazeConfigure
public class MazeConfigure extends Object
Creates MazeClass from given lines surrounded by WallField from all sides (does not need to be in the stream).

Line has to be a series of characters ending with \n.

Types of Field and FieldObject are represented by characters:

  • 'T' ... (target) represented by EndField
  • 'X' ... (wall) represented by WallField
  • 'G' ... (ghost) represented by PathField with GhostObject
  • 'K' ... (key) represented by PathField with KeyObject
  • '.' ... (path) represented by PathField
  • 'S' ... (start) represented by StartField
Author:
Ondřej Vrána
